{"tid":2327225,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[An撚請入] 你哋部An機用手勢導航個陣有冇「黑邊問題」？","createTime":"2020-12-16T02:31:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T10:16:35.000Z","uid":49781,"like":19,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"00380039b95b9237c8edfd587c499585536defea","tid":2327225,"uid":49781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T02:31:50.000Z","msg":"「黑邊問題」即係部機<strong></strong>用緊「手勢導航」個陣，係某啲遊戲或者串流app全螢幕顯示時，即使個導航條縮咗入去都會留低條幼黑邊係底底同左右，就好似咁：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5XuAkPr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5XuAkPr.jpg&h=374d62ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家都知我用Sony機啦，自從Android10有手勢導航後，用Sony機開某啲Games同埋Netflix，只要部機開緊手勢，就會有呢個問題。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然如果隻game/app optimize得好就唔會有事，好似咁：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qOxx7vO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqOxx7vO.jpg&h=27af1596&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(睇得出分別嗎？)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而用返三天皇嘅話就所有game都冇問題。當我以為An11更新會順便搞掂啦，點知都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以我好奇你哋部An機會唔會都有呢個問題，如果你係用緊手勢嘅話？有嘅話係咩牌子咩型號同埋咩game/app？可唔可以留埋個screenshot？<br />\n<br />\n麻煩哂各位巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我部An機冇事，係Sony垃圾<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />An機通病"},{"pid":"c832f3ed9738e3b3ee6c5ff064a1ab5c6e7986a3","tid":2327225,"uid":9838,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T02:33:14.000Z","msg":"sony垃圾不解釋"},{"pid":"1eadca4388e3e30a0453eff32be718448c05affe","tid":2327225,"uid":49781,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c832f3ed9738e3b3ee6c5ff064a1ab5c6e7986a3","tid":2327225,"uid":9838,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T02:33:14.000Z","msg":"sony垃圾不解釋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T02:36:05.000Z","msg":"我淨係想知有冇其他廠都有遇過呢個問題，因為Sony班Staff成日賴鳩啲game developers寫得唔好，而且冇啲傳媒出聲講Sony根本唔撚Care<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我諗呢個問題困擾咗Sony JJ已經有一年"},{"pid":"4785e03183f10f645ceaaaccc967927a157c15cf","tid":2327225,"uid":9838,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T02:54:50.000Z","msg":"無問題，識置中，上下黑邊"},{"pid":"5cb7156721b4dbb8b42fe5152ce87a797b03ee2c","tid":2327225,"uid":202593,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T02:59:51.000Z","msg":"用緊三叔 唔覺有"},{"pid":"c5512aae5b5cf8756e66eb427e21fdc7ccae4053","tid":2327225,"uid":159997,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5cb7156721b4dbb8b42fe5152ce87a797b03ee2c","tid":2327225,"uid":202593,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T02:59:51.000Z","msg":"用緊三叔 唔覺有"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T03:00:17.000Z","msg":"same"},{"pid":"08f994468f415f851dfbe66febdc406671dc3683","tid":2327225,"uid":49781,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4785e03183f10f645ceaaaccc967927a157c15cf","tid":2327225,"uid":9838,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T02:54:50.000Z","msg":"無問題，識置中，上下黑邊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T03:02:54.000Z","msg":"咩機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26ba0e4dbdac6055cbc0273628d1dd4ab80c5c92","tid":2327225,"uid":49781,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T03:16:52.000Z","msg":"負皮個位ching用咩機<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d376a1fb55f88a3cfda522bb2217332fc0009e6","tid":2327225,"uid":219117,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T03:49:30.000Z","msg":"離題講下<br />\n以前用XZ1 果三粒制都係衰過人，不滿咗好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (再以前用compact系列個界面反而好過佢)"},{"pid":"cbe4a4a025510ed62d5c797a609c91e8e1c01aa1","tid":2327225,"uid":127251,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"